1993年12月到1994年1月期间，'''强烈热带气旋雷瓦'''（{{lang-en|Severe Tropical Cyclone Rewa}}）一共在南[[太平洋|太平洋]]迂回行进了28天，先后对6个国家构成影响，共计造成22人死亡。[[热带气旋|气旋]]雷瓦源于12月28日[[诺鲁|诺鲁]]以南洋面的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，并在形成后向西南方向穿越[[所罗门群岛|所罗门群岛]]，从南太平洋盆地穿过[[经度|东经]]160度线进入[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]海域。气旋开始稳步增强并转向南下，其12月31日的行进方向与[[澳洲东岸|澳大利亚东海岸]]基本平行。1月2日，雷瓦达到第一波最高强度，成为四级热带气旋，但这一强度只保持了约12小时就开始因[[风切变|风切变]]增加而减弱。1月4日，风暴转向东南回到南太平洋盆地，并在接下来两天里从[[新喀里多尼亚|新喀里多尼亚]]上空掠过，然后降级成[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]并转朝西北方向移动，于1月10日再次进入澳大利亚海域。

接下来的几天里，气旋表现出重新强化迹象，并且前进路线在[[巴布亚新几内亚|巴布亚新几内亚]]东南方向形成拉长的圆环。雷瓦随后在向东南方向移动的过程中进入快速增强期，达到五级强烈热带气旋的最高强度。之后几天里，风暴回转向西南方向移动并逐渐弱化。有气象监测部门预计雷瓦会从[[昆士兰州|昆士兰州]][[麦凯_(昆士兰州)|麦凯]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但从1月18日开始，气旋与一片上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]发生相互作用并因此转朝东南方向移动，沿昆士兰州海岸擦过。1月20日，雷瓦转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，其残留还在3天后给[[新西兰|新西兰]]带去倾盆大雨。

这场气旋一共夺走了22人的生命，影响的国家和地区包括所罗门群岛、巴布亚新几内亚、澳大利亚东海岸、新喀里多尼亚、[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]]和新西兰。风暴期间，一艘香蕉帆船在前往[[罗塞尔岛|罗塞尔岛]]的途中失踪，船的残骸之后冲到岛上，其上9人估计都已遇难。昆士兰州有3人因风暴引发的交通事故丧生，还有1人被困在排水管道中而死。新喀里多尼亚也有1人死亡，巴布亚新几内亚有8人溺毙。风暴的名称“雷瓦”在热带气旋季过后予以退役，之后都不会再在南太平洋热带气旋命名时采用。

== 气象历史 ==
[[File:Rewa_1993_track.png|thumb]]数据制作的气旋雷瓦路径图。]]
12月26日，[[诺鲁|诺鲁]]东部以南方向约575公里海域的[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]发展出[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]，位于[[楠迪|楠迪]]的[[斐济气象局|斐济气象局]]热带气旋警报中心开始对其进行监控<ref name="Rewa FMS Report">{{cite report |title=Tropical Cyclone Rewa, 26 December 1993 - 21 January 1994 |type=Global tropical/extratropical cyclone climatic atlas |date=1996-06-25 |publisher=Indiana University |author=Fleet Numerical Meteorology and Oceanography Detachment |author2=National Climatic Data Center |deadurl=yes |url=http://webapp1.dlib.indiana.edu/cgi-bin/virtcdlib/index.cgi/4274123/FID1/DATA/TROPIC/SWP_NAR/1993_16.NAR%3B1 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |archivedate=2013-03-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ety848NB?url=http://webapp1.dlib.indiana.edu/cgi-bin/virtcdlib/index.cgi/4274123/FID1/DATA/TROPIC/SWP_NAR/1993_16.NAR;1 }}</ref><ref name="JTWC BT">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-10-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131004155449/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/1994/1994s-bsh/bsh051994.txt | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/1994/1994s-bsh/bsh051994.txt | title = JTWC Tropical Cyclone 05P (Rewa) Best Track Analysis | date = 2002-12-17 | author = Naval Pacific Meteorology and Oceanography Center, Joint Typhoon Warning Center | publisher = United States Navy, United States Air Force | accessdate = 2014-11-25}}</ref>。接下来几天里，低气压因受从北向东的转向气流影响而向西南偏西方向移动，并在这一过程中逐渐发展，组织结构也得到改善<ref name="Rewa FMS Report" /><ref name="DTDSDEC93">{{cite journal | title = December 1993 | journal = Darwin Tropical Diagnostic Statement | year = 1994 | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | volume = 12 | issue = 12 | page = 3 | issn = 1321-4233 | author = Darwin Regional Specialised Meteorological Centre | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/ntregion/statements/tropical/dtds-199312.pdf | accessdate = 2014-11-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102190351/http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/ntregion/statements/tropical/dtds-199312.pdf | deadurl = no | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | archivedate = 2013-11-02}}</ref>。12月28日，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]将低气压归类为第05{{lang|en|P}}号热带低气压，然后楠迪的热带气旋警报中心宣布天气系统已经发展成澳大利亚海域热带气旋强度分级中的一级热带气旋，并将其命名为“雷瓦”（{{lang|en|Rewa}}）<ref name="Hanstrum">{{cite journal | title = The South Pacific and Southeast Indian Ocean Tropical Cyclone Season 1993–94 | author1 = Hanstrum, Barry N | author2 = Smith K.J. | author3 = Bate, Peter W | accessdate = 2014-11-25 | issue = 45 | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | pages = 137–147 | journal = Australian Meteorological and Oceanographic Journal | format = PDF | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/amm/docs/1996/hanstrum.pdf | date = 1996-06-02 | archive-date = 2015-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150923193631/http://www.bom.gov.au/amm/docs/1996/hanstrum.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Wellington BT">{{cite web | date = 2009-05-22 | title = TCWC Wellington Best Track Data 1967–2006 | publisher = International Best Track Archive for Climate Stewardship | author = RSMC Nadi – Tropical Cyclone Centre, TCWC Brisbane, TCWC Wellington | work = Fiji Meteorological Service, Meteorological Service of New Zealand Limited, Australian Bureau of Meteorology | location = United States | accessdate = 2014-11-25 | url = ftp://eclipse.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/ibtracs/original-bt-data-files/wellington/TC_BT_1967_2006.xls}}</ref><ref name="JTWC ATCR">{{cite web | author = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | year = 1995 | accessdate = 2014-11-25 | author2 = Naval Pacific Meteorology and Oceanography Center | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/1994atcr.pdf | title = 1994 Annual Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = United States Navy, United States Air Force | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130221092023/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/1994atcr.pdf | archivedate = 2013-02-21}}</ref>。接下来几天里，由于外界存在有利于热带气旋发展的上层风，系统在向[[罗盘方位|西南偏南]]方向移动的过程中逐渐强化，于12月29日经过[[所罗门群岛|所罗门群岛]]，并对[[巴布亚新几内亚|巴布亚新几内亚]]东南部多个岛屿产生影响<ref name="DTDSDEC93"/><ref name="Rewa TCR">{{cite report | title = Tropical Cyclone Rewa | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140829103257/http://www.bom.gov.au/cyclone/history/rewa.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/cyclone/history/rewa.shtml | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | accessdate = 2014-11-25 | type = Individual Tropical Cyclone Reports | archivedate = 2014-08-29}}</ref>。途经所罗门群岛期间，雷瓦离开南太平洋进入澳大利亚海域，这里属[[澳大利亚气象局|澳大利亚气象局]]驻[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]的热带气旋警报中心预警责任范围<ref name="Hanstrum" /><ref name="Diary">{{cite book | chapter = Rewa: Diary of a tropical cyclone | isbn = 0-642-22435-8 | author1 = Dolan, Chris | author2 = May, Peter | title = Hazard-Wise | publisher = Emergency Management Australia | year = 1995 | page = 59 | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=vHkt7iGw4BUC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | accessdate = 2014-11-25}}</ref>。

12月30日，联合台风警报中心报告称，雷瓦的强度已经可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下达到一级飓风标准，次日清晨，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心报道，系统已经发展成三级强烈热带气旋，并且卫星图像上已经可以看到[[風眼|風眼]]<ref name="Rewa FMS Report" /><ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Wellington BT" />。接下来系统突然大幅转向，并因与上层低压槽发生相互作用而开始沿[[昆士兰州|昆士兰州]]南海岸平行移动<ref name="DTDSDEC93" /><ref name="Hanstrum" />。1月2日，联合台风警报中心和布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心均报告雷瓦已达到最高强度，其中联合台风警报中心报告的[[最大持续风速|一分钟持续风速]]为每小时230公里，相当于萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级下的四级飓风<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Hanstrum" />；而布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心则报告十分钟持续风速每小时205公里，中心气压920[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.17[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），在澳大利亚海域分级中属五级强烈热带气旋<ref name="Hanstrum" />。不过，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心之后在对数据重新加以分析时把风暴的最大持续风速降至每小时175公里，这样雷瓦就只达到四级强烈热带气旋标准<ref name="Wellington BT" /><ref name="Rewa BT">{{cite web | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/tmp/aus199319932.html | title = Tropical Cyclone Rewa Australian region Best Track Analysis | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2013-03-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130310065536/http://www.bom.gov.au/tmp/aus199319932.html | archivedate = 2013-03-10 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。气旋在此强度下保持了约12小时，然后因由北向西的上层气流增强导致系统上空的垂直风切变增多，从1月3日开始减弱<ref>{{cite journal | title = Influence of Environmental Vertical Wind Shear on the Intensity of Hurricane-Strength Tropical Cyclones in the Australian Region | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_monthly-weather-review_2005-12_133_12/page/3644 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | author = Paterson, Linda A | year = 2005 | author2 = Hanstrum, Barry N | author3 = Davidson, Noel E | author4 = Weber, Harry C | volume = 133 | issue = 12 | page = 3644}}</ref><ref name="DTDSJAN94">{{cite journal | journal = Darwin Tropical Diagnostic Statement | year = 1994 | title = January 1994 | publisher = Australian Bureau of Meteorology | volume = 13 | issue = 1 | page = 2 | issn = 1321-4233 | author = Darwin Regional Specialised Meteorological Centre | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105003916/http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/ntregion/statements/tropical/dtds-199401.pdf | url = http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/ntregion/statements/tropical/dtds-199401.pdf | accessdate = 2014-11-26}}</ref>。这一天里气旋总体向南面偏东方向移动，之后又在逼近[[经度|东经]]160°线后略向东面转向<ref name="Rewa TCR"/>。

1月4日，雷瓦回转进入南太平洋并继续东进，这时其强度已降至三级强烈热带气旋级别，并且还在继续减弱，楠迪的热带气旋警报中心估计系统的十分钟持续风速约为每小时150公里<ref name="Wellington BT" />。次日，由于[[新喀里多尼亚|新喀里多尼亚]]的山脉产生炎热而干燥的[[焚风|焚风]]，对气旋环流造成不利影响，其风眼也因此变得模糊<ref name="Rewa FMS Report" />。楠迪的热带气旋警报中心在报告中称，系统已弱化成二级热带气旋，而联合台风警报中心则认为雷瓦已经降级为热带风暴<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。气旋随后在新喀里多尼亚西南海岸的圣文森特湾（{{lang|en|Saint Vincent Bay}}）附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，再于1月6日从蒂奥（{{lang|en|Thio}}）附近重回大海<ref name="Rewa FMS Report" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。到1月7日时，由于受到从北向西的上层气流影响，雷瓦的环流已经暴露出来，为此联合台风警报中心和楠迪的热带气旋警报中心均报告称气旋已经降级成热带低气压<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。之后的3天里，系统的残余下层环流因受[[新西兰|新西兰]]和[[克马德克群岛|克马德克群岛]]之间强烈[[高气压|高气压区]]产生的东南向[[信风|信风]]影响而转向西北<ref name="Rewa FMS Report" /><ref name="DTDSJAN94" />。1月10日，雷瓦的残留离开南太平洋再次进入澳大利亚海域，并在这一过程中因澳大利亚东部海域上空的中到上层低压槽规模增大而开始重新增强成热带气旋<ref name="Rewa TCR" /><ref name="DTDSJAN94" />。

进入澳大利亚海域后，风暴先是向西北方向前进，之后转向北上，其路径形成巨大的圆弧，联合台风警报中心和[[莫尔兹比港|莫尔兹比港]]的热带气旋警报中心于1月13日宣布，系统已在巴布亚新几内亚南部岛屿附近再度强化成热带气旋<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。当晚，雷瓦在[[塔古拉岛|塔古拉岛]]附近向顺时针方向急剧转向，开始向东南方向、布里斯班热带气旋警报中心责任范围进发，并在这一过程中进一步增强<ref name="Rewa TCR" />。1月15日，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心报告称，气旋已经再次增强成三级强烈热带气旋，而联合台风警报中心则报告雷瓦已经再次达到一级飓风标准<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Wellington BT" />。当晚，由于有上层低压槽逼近，风暴开始爆发性增强。次日，联合台风警报中心称系统已经达到一分钟持续风速每小时230公里的最高强度<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心也在这天晚些时候称雷瓦的十分钟持续风速为每小时205公里，这已经达到澳大利亚海域的五级强烈热带气旋标准<ref name="Rewa BT" />。达到最高强度后，系统回转向西南偏南方向移动并开始逐渐减弱<ref name="JTWC BT" />。到了1月18日，联合台风警报中心称雷瓦已经降至热带风暴强度，但布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心仍坚持认为雷瓦在这天尚属三级强烈热带气旋<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。次日，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心称，风暴已减弱成二级热带气旋，并回转向东南方向移动，行进至[[昆士兰州|昆士兰州]][[麦凯_(昆士兰州)|麦凯]]以东约265公里洋面<ref name="Rewa TCR" /><ref name="Wellington BT" />。系统在接下来两天里强度基本保持稳定，并沿昆士兰州海岸向东南偏南方向前进<ref name="Wellington BT" />。1月21日，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心和联合台风警报中心报道，雷瓦已经第三次（也是最后一次）进入南太平洋，并且强度已低于热带气旋标准<ref name="Hanstrum" /><ref name="JTWC ATCR" />。1月23日，位于[[惠灵顿|惠灵顿]]的热带气旋警报中心发现风暴残留的踪迹，新西兰降下暴雨，系统最终在惠灵顿以东约400公里海域上空消散<ref name="Hanstrum" /><ref name="Wellington BT" /><ref name="DTDSJAN94" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
气旋雷瓦先后对所罗门群岛、巴布亚新几内亚、澳大利亚东海岸、新喀里多尼亚、[[瓦努阿图|瓦努阿图]]和新西兰部分地区构成影响，一共夺走了22人的生命<ref name="AAP1">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZoIuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TKEFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4299,2800343&dq=cyclone+rewa&hl=en | title = Cyclone ravages Australia | date = 1994-01-20 | agency = Australian Associated Press | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | newspaper = Reading Eagle | archive-date = 2019-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190305001601/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZoIuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TKEFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4299,2800343&dq=cyclone+rewa&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由于风暴造成了严重影响，其名称“雷瓦”之后予以退役，永远都不会再在南太平洋热带气旋命名时采用<ref name="SPAC TCOP">{{cite web | title = Tropical Cyclone Operational Plan for the South-East Indian Ocean and the Southern Pacific Ocean | author = RA V Tropical Cyclone Committee | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/TCP-24_RAVOpPlan_2010.pdf | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927082539/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/TCP-24_RAVOpPlan_2010.pdf | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | format = PDF | date = 2011-05-23 | accessdate = 2014-11-26}}</ref>。

=== 所罗门群岛、新喀里多尼亚、瓦努阿图和新西兰 ===
12月28至30日，所罗门群岛受到正在发展的雷瓦袭击，是第一个受这场风暴影响的[[岛屿国家|岛国]]<ref name="Sol">{{cite web|url=http://www.met.gov.sb/tcnames.pdf |title=Tropical Cyclones/Depressions that passed through Solomon Islands Region |publisher=Solomon Islands Meteorological Service |date=2009-09-13 |accessdate=2012-10-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030195156/http://www.met.gov.sb/tcnames.pdf |archivedate=2012-10-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。12月28日系统成为热带气旋时正从该国[[马莱塔省|马莱塔省]]的外围[[环礁|环礁]]以北经过，风暴接下来又掠过[[马莱塔岛|马莱塔岛]]的最南端上空，再于12月29日从[[瓜达尔卡纳尔岛|瓜达尔卡纳尔岛]]以南和[[拉纳尔岛|拉纳尔岛]]以北经过<ref name="JTWC BT" /><ref name="Rewa TCR" />。

1月5日，气旋雷瓦开始影响新喀里多尼亚，再于当晚从[[新喀里多尼亚|格朗特尔岛]]上空经过<ref name="MFNC" />。该群岛部分地区降雨量超过300毫米，所有的主要河流都因此出现泛滥<ref name="MFNC">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101022258/http://www.meteo.nc/cyclone/cyclones-passes?view=cyclones |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.meteo.nc/cyclone/cyclones-passes?view=cyclones |author=New Caledonia Meteorological Office |title=Cyclone Passes Entre 1950 et 1995: Rewa |publisher=Météo-France |accessdate=2014-11-26 |archivedate=2014-11-01 }}</ref><ref name="Earthweek">{{cite news | author = Newmann, Steve | newspaper = The Sunday Gazette | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WNtQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=n-kMAAAAIBAJ&dq=cyclone%20rewa&pg=5914%2C1965524 | title = Earthweek: a diary of the planet for the week ending 7 January 1994 | date = 1994-01-09 | accessdate = 2014-11-26}}</ref>。新喀里多尼亚发生多起山体滑坡，还有1人丧生，[[洛亚蒂群岛|洛亚蒂群岛]]的[[马雷岛|马雷岛]]上一处海港的部分海港墙被风暴产生的大浪摧毁<ref name="MFNC" />。

12月28日，系统经过所罗门群岛期间没有对瓦努阿图构成影响，但到了1月5日气旋经过新喀里多尼亚后还是对瓦努阿图的南部多个岛屿产生了影响<ref name="Vanuatu">{{cite report | deadurl = yes | title = Tropical cyclones in Vanuatu: 1847 to 1994 | publisher = Vanuatu Meteorological Service | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | date = 1994-05-19 | url = http://www.pacificdisaster.net/pdnadmin/data/original/VUT_TC_1847_1994.pdf | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002161450/http://www.pacificdisaster.net/pdnadmin/data/original/VUT_TC_1847_1994.pdf }}</ref>。1月6至8日，雷瓦向北面偏西方向前进，给[[塔菲亚省|塔菲亚省]]部分地区带去大风，其强度接近[[蒲福风级|烈风]]标准<ref name="Vanuatu" />。1月8至9日，气旋从[[维拉港|维拉港]]东南方向约175公里洋面经过，给[[埃法特岛|埃法特岛]]带去强烈的西北风和大浪，对港口的[[潮间带|潮间带]]构成破坏<ref name="Vanuatu" />。

1月19至24日，风暴残留、[[菲奥德兰|菲奥德兰]]上空缓慢移动的[[锋_(气象)|锋]]，以及一场南风暴共同作用，导致新西兰南部岛屿普降暴雨并引发洪灾<ref name="Niwa">{{cite web | title = January 1994 South Island Ex-tropical Cyclone Rewa | url = http://hwe.niwa.co.nz/event/January_1994_South_Island_Ex-tropical_Cyclone_Rewa | work = New Zealand Historic Weather Events Catalog | publisher = National Institute of Water and Atmospheric Research | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103021036/http://hwe.niwa.co.nz/event/January_1994_South_Island_Ex-tropical_Cyclone_Rewa | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | date = 2013-03-10}}</ref>。1月21日，该国韦斯特兰区、菲奥德兰和南部湖区出现洪区和多起山体滑坡，还有许多道路和桥梁受损<ref name="Niwa" />。

=== 巴布亚新几内亚 ===
气旋雷瓦存在期间先后两次对巴布亚新几内亚构成影响，首先是在12月28日至次年1月1日，第二次则是1月12至14日<ref name="Rewa TCR" /><ref name="SPAC">{{cite book | author = Terry, James P | publisher = Springer | date = 2007-10-29 | isbn = 978-0-387-71542-1 | title = Tropical cyclones: climatology and impacts in the South Pacific | url = http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=CUh3FXQFiDMC&pg=PA47&dq=%22Cyclone+Rewa%22&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22Cyclone%20Rewa%22&f=false | page = 47 | accessdate = 2014-11-27 | archive-date = 2016-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307215242/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=CUh3FXQFiDMC&pg=PA47&dq=%22Cyclone+Rewa%22&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22Cyclone%20Rewa%22&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴来袭前，塔古拉岛、罗塞尔岛和[[萨马赖|萨马赖岛]]收到了[[热带气旋警告|气旋预警和警报]]，有关部门呼吁人们不要前往海滩<ref name="AAP1" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Nine Missing In Cyclone | date = 1993-12-31 | agency = The Associated Press}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref><ref name="PNG Floods">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304123644/http://trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/127257496 | deadurl = no | url = http://trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/127257496 | title = PNG floods: death toll eases but thousands more homeless. | newspaper = The Canberra Times | date = 1993-12-31 | accessdate = 2014-11-26 | page = 6 | publisher = National Library of Australia | archivedate = 2014-03-04}}</ref>。接下来雷瓦产生的暴雨、大浪和时速达100公里的大风又对包括塔古拉岛、罗塞尔岛和萨马赖岛在内的群岛部分地区构成影响<ref name="AAP1" /><ref name="9miss">{{cite news | title = Nine missing after cyclone hits png | date = 1994-01-19 | agency = [[新华社|Xinhua News Agency]]}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。受灾最严重的地区集中在主要河流沿线附近社区，气旋导致多条道路阻塞、多座桥梁与一所教堂、以及许多民房和庭院被毁，包括[[咖啡|咖啡]]和[[椰子核|椰子]]在内的部分重要作物也毁于一旦<ref name="PNG Floods" /><ref name="floods">{{cite news | title = Floods Kill at Least 8, More than 1,000 Homeless | date = 1993-12-30 | agency = The Australian Associated Press}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。风暴在这些地区一共造成17人死亡，其中8人属溺毙，另有约3500人无家可归<ref name="PNG Floods" /><ref name="floods" />。一艘香蕉帆船在前往罗塞尔岛的途中因遇上大浪失踪<ref name="9miss" /><ref name="13 dead">{{cite news | title = 13 Dead in cyclone | page = 17 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TJcVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=CwsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1964%2C2992368 | accessdate = 2014-11-27 | newspaper = Manila Standard | agency = Associated Press | date = 1994-01-21}}</ref>，地方虽有组织搜救，但他们只发现船的残骸，该国救灾应急部门估计船上9人均已遇难<ref name="AAP1" /><ref name="13 dead" /><ref name="9miss" />。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]12月30日凌晨0点，[[罗塞尔岛|罗塞尔岛]]上的一处自动气象站测得每小时55公里的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Tropical Cyclone Weekly Summary #126 (26 December 1993 – 2 January 1994) | url = https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/sci.geo.meteorology/Vq8-iSenz4Q | date = 1994-01-07 | accessdate = 2014-11-27 | author = Beven II, John L | publisher = Florida State University | archive-date = 2013-08-02 | archive-url = https://archive.today/20130802023140/https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=%23!topic/javaposse/TLNrMsznjRY#!topic/sci.geo.meteorology/Vq8-iSenz4Q | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

=== 澳大利亚 ===
1994年初，气旋雷瓦在南下期间曾沿昆士兰州海岸平行移动，但由于其位置距陆地尚远，在麦凯东部以北约600公里处，因此没有对该州产生任何直接影响<ref name="Wellington BT" /><ref name="No relief">{{cite news | publisher = Nationwide News Pty Limited | title = No relief near for heat-weary state | author = Smith, A | date = 1994-01-05 | agency = Courier-Mail}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。风暴产生的大浪对部分沿海地区构成间接影响，多人因此需要救援才能脱困，这种情况一直到1月4日气旋开始朝新喀里多尼亚移动后才结束<ref name="Earthweek" /><ref name="No relief" />。雷瓦开始再次影响昆士兰州时，布里斯班的热带气旋警报中心向该州多个区域发布预警和警报，并预计风暴会在麦凯附近登陆<ref name="Diary" /><ref name="Alert">{{cite news | newspaper = The Adelaide Advertiser | title = Queensland on Cyclone Rewa alert | date = 1994-01-19 | publisher = Nationwide News Pty Limited}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref>。1月18日，地方灾害委员会举行会晤，考虑是否要将居民撤离，还有[[直升机|直升机]]前去告知那些正在国家公园度假的人们做好准备<ref name="Alert" />。[[肖尔沃特湾|肖尔沃特湾]]（{{lang|en|Shoalwater Bay}}）正在举行的军事演习被迫中止，军事人员疏散到[[洛坎普顿|洛坎普顿]]，以免受到洪水的威胁<ref name="Alert" />。海岸沿线有包括[[格拉德斯通_(昆士兰州)|格拉德斯通]]在内的多个港口予以关闭，并告知大型船只暂时留在海上，小型船只则应加固，做好防范风暴来袭的准备<ref name="Alert" />。

1月19日，雷瓦开始给昆士兰州带去倾盆大雨和风暴强度大风，给海岸沿线造成一定程度破坏<ref name="Rewa TCR" />。不过，气旋并没有像之前预测的那样登陆麦凯，而是回转向东南偏南方向移动，最近时距海岸仅有不到100公里<ref name="Rewa TCR" /><ref name="easing" />。[[耶蓬|耶蓬]]近海有艘拖网渔船因遇上雷瓦产生的大浪导致螺旋槳受损，并且铁锚的链条也被扯断，船上两名男子只能顺水飘流、听天由命，所幸他们之后都由陆军[[UH-60黑鹰直升机|黑鹰直升机]]所救<ref name="easing">{{cite news | title = QLD battered as cyclone eases | date = 1994-01-20 | newspaper = Sydney Morning Herald | author = Tom, Emma | page = 4}}{{subscription required | via = Lexis Nexis}}</ref><ref name="impacts">{{cite journal | title = Tropical Cyclone Impacts along the Australian east coast from November to April 1858 to 2000 | publisher = Australian Severe Weather | author = Callaghan, Jeff | url = http://australiasevereweather.com.au/cyclones/impacts-eastcoast.pdf | accessdate = 2014-11-27 | date = 2004-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110405102413/http://australiasevereweather.com.au/cyclones/impacts-eastcoast.pdf | archivedate = 2011-04-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[埃利奥特夫人岛|埃利奥特夫人岛]]受灾最为严重，受到气旋风力的强烈冲击；[[赫伦岛|赫伦岛]]有多种珍稀树木和鸟类栖息地不是完全被毁就是严重受损。1月19日，雷瓦与上层低压槽发生相互作用，给布里斯班和[[黄金海岸_(澳大利亚)|黄金海岸]]部分区域带去暴雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]<ref name="Brisbane flooding">{{cite web|author=Queensland Hydrology Section |title=Queensland Flood Summary 1990 – 1999 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.bom.gov.au/qld/flood/fld_history/floodsum_1990.shtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102174710/http://www.bom.gov.au/qld/flood/fld_history/floodsum_1990.shtml |archivedate=2014-11-02 |publisher=Australian Bureau of Meteorology |year=2010 |accessdate=2014-11-27 }}</ref>。布里斯班在6小时内的降雨量就超过144毫米，导致该市4人丧生，并出现局部洪灾<ref name="impacts" /><ref name="Brisbane flooding" />。有3人是因交通事故死亡，另1人在洪水中冲浪，结果困在排水管道中溺毙<ref name="impacts" /><ref>{{cite news|title=New threat as cyclone whirls out to sea |url=http://newsstore.fairfax.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=nstore&kw=Cyclone+Rewa&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=news940121_0166_7969 |accessdate=2014-11-27 |newspaper=The Age |date=1994-01-21 |author=Tom, Emma |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107114221/http://newsstore.fairfax.com.au/apps/viewDocument.ac?page=1&sy=nstore&kw=Cyclone%20Rewa&pb=all_ffx&dt=selectRange&dr=entire&so=relevance&sf=text&sf=headline&rc=10&rm=200&sp=nrm&clsPage=1&docID=news940121_0166_7969 |archivedate=2014-01-07 |page=6 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。整个布里斯班有约100套民宅和20辆汽车因洪水受损，[[西澳大利亚州|西澳大利亚州]]对抗昆士兰州的[[谢菲尔德盾|谢菲尔德盾]][[板球|板球]]比赛予以推迟，比赛场馆已经因洪水变得类似于小型湖泊<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Australian Government | author = Attorney-General's Department | accessdate = 2012-03-31 | date = 2011-05-05 | title = Disasters Database: Disaster Event Details: Cyclone Rewa | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.disasters.ema.gov.au/Browse%20Details/DisasterEventDetails.aspx?DisasterEventID=549 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120331100902/http://www.disasters.ema.gov.au/Browse%20Details/DisasterEventDetails.aspx?DisasterEventID=549 | archivedate = 2012-03-31}}</ref>。

